about.heading: About
about.details:
Hi, I'm Younès, a frontend developer, who located in France.
I'm Constantly looking for a new challenging opportunity surrounded by wonderful talented people trying to push the bounderies the best they could. Also, the creative part is really important in the equation.
For the last eight years, I've worked on Freelancing and corporate on many applications and software prototype for touch interface and web application.
You can find some of my open source code on GitHub, and technical posts on Tumblr.
